<p>I don‚Äôt think I need to tell what is it, but in case you are still wondering, it‚Äôs <em>Tea</em>.</p>

<p>Today, in this article, let‚Äôs learn how to make a good cup of tea and how you can adjust it to your needs as required. Let‚Äôs get started, shall we?</p>

<h3 id="ingredient-list">Ingredient List</h3>
<ul>
  <li>100ml water</li>
  <li>300ml milk</li>
  <li>1tbsp tea leaves</li>
  <li>1tbsp sugar</li>
  <li>1 cardamom</li>
  <li>1 inch ginger</li>
  <li>Love ‚ô•Ô∏è</li>
</ul>

